Content card - NYT - CloudM Rooftop bar

title.en-US: Experience the clouds at CloudM Rooftop bar

content.value: cloudM is a rooftop bar located in the citizenM hotel in Times Square 1. The bar offers a stunning view of the city skyline and is known for its craft cocktails and wine classes. The bar is located on the 21st floor of the hotel and is decorated with chic and art-infused interiors. The menu features a wide range of drinks, including craft cocktails, wines, and beers, and the food menu includes small plates and tapas.

altText.en-US: Our CloudM CitizenM rooftop bar at Times square NYC

caption.en-US: Our CloudM CitizenM rooftop bar at Times square NYC

content.value: Make our living room your office! Choose form two easy-to-reach New York locations ‚Äì Times Square and Bowery ‚Äì¬†both perfect for creatives and entrepreneurs, just like you.
These inspiring co-working spaces come with cafe-style and long table seating options, superfast Wi-Fi, free filtered water, power outlets and plenty of food and drink options.
Remember, this is your community ‚Äì make yourself at home!

The Crossroads of the World... Midtown Manhattan... the core of the Big Apple. Whatever you call Times Square, you'll be right in the center of it in our art-filled living room. Strike the perfect work/fun balance with our rooftop bar ‚Äì perfect for impromptu business meetings (or an after-work date). And when you need a time out, Central Park is only 15 minutes away!

Hello, Lower East Side! Just an 18-min train from Grand Central Station, our Bowery hotel is perfectly placed ‚Äì away from big crowds, but still close to big fun. Outside: Chinatown and Little Italy on the left, SoHo in front, Greenwich Village to the right. Need to unwind? Take the lift to our cloudM rooftop bar for stunning views of the Manhattan skyline.
